plot: 060 : Bulma tricks the soldiers who captured her and reclaims the Dragon Balls; Goku trains using Kaio-Ken in 100 times normal gravity; Krillin and Gohan continue their way to Guru; Frieza is informed the Ginyu Force is on its way.

Bulma tricks the soldiers in an attempt to reclaim the Dragon Ball; Goku trains with Kaioken under 100 times normal gravity; Vegeta follows Krillin and Gohan as they continue to Guru; Frieza gets a report that the Ginyu Force is on its way.—Zabon
